I '''Leonard Max Adleman''' (mibait Disiembri 31, 1945) metung yang  [[theoretical computer science|theoretical computer scientist]] ampong professor ning [[computer science]] aat [[molecular biology]] king [[University ning Southern California]]. Kebaluan ya bilang metung kareng talaimbentu ning [[RSA]] (Rivest-Shamir-Adleman) cryptosystem inyang 1977, na ning [[DNA computing]]. Ing RSA maleparan yang magagamit kareng [[computer security|securidad]] pangcomuter, kayabe ne ing [[https]].

Mibait king [[California]], i Adleman meragul ya king [[San Francisco]], ampong megaral ya king  [[University ning California, Berkeley]], nung nu atanggap ne ing kayang [[Bachelor of Arts|BA]] degree keng [[mathematicu]] inyang 1968 ampo ing kayang [[Doctor of Philosophy|Ph.D.]] degree king [[EECS]] inyang 1976.

